    "Executive function 'warm-up' tasks (easy, familiar cognitive exercises in the 5 minutes before demanding work) activate the relevant prefrontal networks without depleting resources — the PFC, like any physical system, performs better when brought gradually to operating temperature rather than launched cold into maximum load.",
